WEBVTT

00:00.711 --> 00:02.192
I was born here.

00:02.205 --> 00:03.722
I grew up here. My friends are here,

00:03.746 --> 00:05.998
my work is here. There's
only one way I'm leaving now

00:06.045 --> 00:07.487
and that's in a coffin.

00:07.607 --> 00:08.841
That's good to know.

00:09.267 --> 00:10.767
It's better if you go back to your mum.

00:10.790 --> 00:12.302
But you said this is my home.

00:13.586 --> 00:15.494
- Tom!
- I'll drop your things round later.

00:16.055 --> 00:18.565
- Tom!
- I never want to see him again.

00:20.264 --> 00:22.225
You're not going to waste 15 years.

00:22.581 --> 00:24.285
Tonight's when you escape.

00:24.857 --> 00:26.036
What's going on?

00:26.235 --> 00:28.277
- You're not taking her.
- You're never going to see me again.

00:28.324 --> 00:29.941
- Come on!
- You're never going to see Amelie again.

00:29.981 --> 00:31.645
- You're obsessed.
- Please, Kate.

00:31.662 --> 00:32.998
Have her!

00:35.368 --> 00:37.924
My daughter! My family!

00:37.953 --> 00:40.288
- I didn't do any of that.
- No, no,

00:40.340 --> 00:42.185
- no!
- Your wife and your daughter have moved away.

00:42.196 --> 00:44.466
Your mother is dead and
you threw your own son out

00:44.508 --> 00:47.659
- so there's nothing left for you here.
- You think you've won.

00:47.940 --> 00:49.404
Look, I'm still here.

00:50.653 --> 00:51.674
Where are you going?

00:51.715 --> 00:53.145
To get my son.

00:53.991 --> 00:55.369
We need to talk.

